  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Too busy being fun to worry about looking good.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ephialtes drops the player right into the action. Each nightmare contains a menacing antagonist who plays by their own rules. It's your job to figure them out. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4159490/extras/131585727ad61808d165eaea65485474.poster.avif?t=1774109815\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4159490/extras/131585727ad61808d165eaea65485474.webm?t=1774109815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4159490/extras/131585727ad61808d165eaea65485474.mp4?t=1774109815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Missions & Best Time:</strong> Each nightmare has three optional missions you can complete as well as has your best time recorded so you can attempt to beat it. Meaning facing your nightmares is never truly over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4159490/extras/9ad08e4613c4b3b656f6ffe42358e8fc.poster.avif?t=1774109815\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4159490/extras/9ad08e4613c4b3b656f6ffe42358e8fc.webm?t=1774109815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4159490/extras/9ad08e4613c4b3b656f6ffe42358e8fc.mp4?t=1774109815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Too busy being fun to worry about looking good.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ephialtes drops the player right into the action. Each nightmare contains a menacing antagonist who plays by their own rules. It's your job to figure them out. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4159490/extras/131585727ad61808d165eaea65485474.poster.avif?t=1774109815\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4159490/extras/131585727ad61808d165eaea65485474.webm?t=1774109815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4159490/extras/131585727ad61808d165eaea65485474.mp4?t=1774109815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Missions & Best Time:</strong> Each nightmare has three optional missions you can complete as well as has your best time recorded so you can attempt to beat it. Meaning facing your nightmares is never truly over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4159490/extras/9ad08e4613c4b3b656f6ffe42358e8fc.poster.avif?t=1774109815\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4159490/extras/9ad08e4613c4b3b656f6ffe42358e8fc.webm?t=1774109815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4159490/extras/9ad08e4613c4b3b656f6ffe42358e8fc.mp4?t=1774109815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
